1
00:00:00,041 --> 00:00:02,711
You said you'd grant my wish.

2
00:00:06,506 --> 00:00:11,136
Can you kiss me?

3
00:00:11,511 --> 00:00:13,888
Stop with the drunken nonsense.

4
00:00:13,888 --> 00:00:15,306
Don't do something you'll regret.

5
00:00:16,016 --> 00:00:17,726
I'm serious, though.

6
00:00:19,352 --> 00:00:23,606
If you do, I won't bother you anymore.

7
00:00:23,648 --> 00:00:28,403
If you grant my wish, I'll do whatever you say, Teacher.

8
00:00:28,987 --> 00:00:31,573
You know I always listen to you.

9
00:00:36,077 --> 00:00:38,038
You're promising me.

10
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,790
That you'll do exactly as I say.

11
00:00:53,887 --> 00:00:54,929
What?

12
00:00:56,181 --> 00:00:58,641
I'm not a kid.

13
00:00:58,975 --> 00:01:01,811
I can tell the difference between a peck and a kiss.

14
00:01:39,057 --> 00:01:40,475
Are you sobering up?

15
00:01:41,184 --> 00:01:43,311
Why am I at your house, Teacher?

16
00:01:44,062 --> 00:01:45,438
Don't you remember?

17
00:01:53,863 --> 00:01:55,824
If you're sober, go home.

18
00:01:55,824 --> 00:01:57,450
I'll call you a cab.

19
00:02:04,749 --> 00:02:07,544
Actually, I remember everything.

20
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:10,839
I was afraid you'd run away again if I said I remembered,

21
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:13,299
so I lied.

22
00:02:15,593 --> 00:02:17,095
Then you must know what I'm going to say.

23
00:02:17,387 --> 00:02:18,429
I don't want to hear it.

24
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,389
Don't.

25
00:02:23,768 --> 00:02:25,311
Just hold back for a year.

26
00:02:26,062 --> 00:02:28,523
We only have one year left to see each other at school anyway.

27
00:02:32,819 --> 00:02:35,905
I really don't know what to do.

28
00:02:36,239 --> 00:02:38,867
What am I supposed to do?

29
00:02:38,867 --> 00:02:41,578
How can I stop liking you?

30
00:02:41,578 --> 00:02:43,913
You don't know either, Teacher.

31
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:46,124
Jaeon.

32
00:02:52,005 --> 00:02:53,840
I think you're still a bit drunk.

33
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:55,175
No.

34
00:02:55,175 --> 00:02:56,968
I'm completely sober.

35
00:02:56,968 --> 00:03:00,305
I'm not just saying this because I'm drunk.

36
00:03:00,305 --> 00:03:02,432
Are you trying to run away again like last time?

37
00:03:04,309 --> 00:03:05,602
Are you going to pretend you don't know again?

38
00:03:05,602 --> 00:03:09,439
Are you going to deny it?

39
00:03:09,856 --> 00:03:12,817
You ran away just because I confessed that I like you.

40
00:03:12,817 --> 00:03:13,651
And just because we kissed once,

41
00:03:13,651 --> 00:03:15,570
you act like you'll never see me again.

42
00:03:15,904 --> 00:03:19,115
I want to confess my feelings seriously like an adult too,

43
00:03:19,115 --> 00:03:21,701
but what can I do when it's not working?

44
00:03:21,701 --> 00:03:24,954
I'm scared you'll run away if I don't throw a fit.

45
00:03:25,205 --> 00:03:30,501
I don't really know how you ended up liking me,

46
00:03:30,877 --> 00:03:35,590
but it's because I'm not confident I can love you back.

47
00:03:38,134 --> 00:03:42,013
Do you still like him?

48
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:44,933
Is that why you're rejecting me?

49
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:46,684
Is there no room for me?

50
00:03:46,684 --> 00:03:48,436
No.

51
00:03:49,604 --> 00:03:53,358
I've already completely moved on from Yujun.

52
00:03:54,817 --> 00:03:57,528
It has nothing to do with that.

53
00:04:07,747 --> 00:04:11,209
It's just that I don't have the confidence.

54
00:04:11,584 --> 00:04:14,254
What if I never end up liking you back?

55
00:04:14,963 --> 00:04:18,716
If we just end up as an unrequited love,

56
00:04:18,716 --> 00:04:20,802
why should you be the one getting hurt when you did nothing wrong?

57
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:21,761
I won't get hurt.

58
00:04:21,761 --> 00:04:24,097
You will.

59
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:26,474
You will.

60
00:04:26,474 --> 00:04:28,559
So...

61
00:04:33,022 --> 00:04:35,358
So it's a relationship we just shouldn't start.

62
00:04:40,446 --> 00:04:43,574
Jaeon.

63
00:04:43,574 --> 00:04:46,661
Let's just stay as a good hyung and dongsaeng,

64
00:04:46,661 --> 00:04:49,747
as a good teacher and student.

65
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:54,627
You shouldn't have said that.

66
00:04:57,964 --> 00:05:00,717
You shouldn't have said that you don't dislike me.

67
00:05:01,342 --> 00:05:03,553
It's not for your sake, it's for mine.

68
00:05:03,553 --> 00:05:06,723
You're saying all this because you're worried I'll get hurt.

69
00:05:07,307 --> 00:05:09,392
You shouldn't be so sweet to me then.

70
00:05:09,475 --> 00:05:12,145
Why did you kiss me just because I asked you to?

71
00:05:13,521 --> 00:05:14,939
You're being unreasonable.

72
00:05:15,064 --> 00:05:17,775
It just makes me unable to give up.

73
00:05:17,775 --> 00:05:20,737
It makes me want to make you like me no matter what.

74
00:05:20,737 --> 00:05:21,487
You know my personality.

75
00:05:21,487 --> 00:05:23,865
You know how competitive I am.

76
00:05:26,409 --> 00:05:28,244
It was all my first time.

77
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:31,956
Liking someone,

78
00:05:31,956 --> 00:05:33,958
and kissing... it was all my first time.

79
00:05:34,584 --> 00:05:38,838
How can I just give up so easily?

80
00:05:46,554 --> 00:05:48,556
See?

81
00:05:48,556 --> 00:05:53,186
How can you tell me to give up when you're being so sweet?

82
00:05:56,647 --> 00:05:59,275
Don't you think you're completely blinded by love?

83
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:04,197
The only person who calls me sweet

84
00:06:04,197 --> 00:06:05,782
is you.

85
00:06:06,074 --> 00:06:08,785
Then I guess I am blinded.

86
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:11,913
I love everything you do, Teacher.

87
00:06:13,873 --> 00:06:16,167
I just love you.

88
00:06:18,252 --> 00:06:21,297
I won't throw a fit begging you to like me.

89
00:06:22,548 --> 00:06:24,550
You're throwing a fit right now.

90
00:06:28,638 --> 00:06:30,223
Then will you date me?

91
00:06:31,641 --> 00:06:32,725
We'll see.

92
00:06:33,601 --> 00:06:35,978
Depends on how you act.

93
00:06:38,398 --> 00:06:40,733
Try to win me over.

94
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:41,859
I might just fall for it.

95
00:06:44,737 --> 00:06:47,365
Are you sure you're the adult here?

96
00:06:47,365 --> 00:06:49,200
Why do you keep teasing me?

97
00:06:53,788 --> 00:06:56,749
I guess it's just because you're cute...

98
00:07:23,776 --> 00:07:28,030
Why were you waiting?

99
00:07:32,368 --> 00:07:34,620
Teacher.

100
00:07:36,789 --> 00:07:37,790
Yeah.

101
00:07:40,793 --> 00:07:42,420
I like you.

102
00:07:45,715 --> 00:07:47,216
I thought you said you wouldn't throw a fit.

103
00:07:48,885 --> 00:07:50,720
I'm talking in my sleep.

104
00:07:53,055 --> 00:07:55,016
I know you're not sleeping.

105
00:08:06,694 --> 00:08:09,197
You just thought about kissing me, didn't you?

106
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:15,286
That's just in your head.

107
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:50,905
Teacher.

108
00:08:51,364 --> 00:08:52,281
Yeah.

109
00:08:52,615 --> 00:08:53,449
What?

110
00:08:53,449 --> 00:08:54,951
You're not even surprised.

111
00:08:54,951 --> 00:08:56,827
Why would I be surprised by this?

112
00:08:56,827 --> 00:08:57,370
Heading to class?

113
00:08:57,370 --> 00:08:58,162
Yeah.

114
00:08:58,162 --> 00:09:00,164
Do you have a class too, Teacher?

115
00:09:00,164 --> 00:09:02,250
Yeah.

116
00:09:08,965 --> 00:09:11,425
We're at school.

117
00:09:11,425 --> 00:09:14,220
There's no one around.

118
00:09:18,558 --> 00:09:19,642
Just for today.

119
00:09:22,395 --> 00:09:25,398
But how long are you going to keep calling me Teacher?

120
00:09:25,398 --> 00:09:28,401
If not Teacher, what should I call you?

121
00:09:28,401 --> 00:09:32,780
Should I call you Hyung?

122
00:09:33,739 --> 00:09:34,907
Professor.

123
00:09:34,907 --> 00:09:35,533
No way.

124
00:09:35,533 --> 00:09:36,033
Hyung.

125
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,993
Hyung!
